<br>
This guild is member oriented.<br>
Our goal is to take Care of our own....and care is Not defined as uber twinking, or power leveling as a rule. We are simply a bunch that think there is much in EQ that is lost in the politics and BS that is associated with many guilds, and in dealing with some of the personalities that infest our server. We have been on this server, in a secret conclave for almost a year now, the establishment of Catharsis is simply a manner of &quot;going public&quot; as it were.<br>
<br>
The reason our above posted Mission Statement is so strongly stated is because we are intrested only in brave, no-nonsense players who realized that Role Playing is fun, fine and dandy, but in the end we are all here to eventually kill Dragons and whatever is out there. <br>
<br>
Plat is a way to a means, not the reason we play. Leveling is a means to a way, and only opens doors that are otherwise closed to us, but in the process we realize that it is who we are associated with that makes the play enjoyable.......not the level or the Mobile Object (mob) or the loot.<br>
<br>
Anyone of us will tell you, if the above agenda intimidates you, then you are most assuredly not going to do well, or be happy, in this guild. PvP is not our goal, it is a way of telling the 10 year olds (and those with a 10 year old mentality) that we are not to be trifled with. We are here to enjoy all that EQ has to offer ...... adventure, friendship, camaradierie, (and if you ever see some of my screenshots) the beauty of it. <br>
<br>
We are not here to tolerate the tantrums, theives, and all around BS espoused by the immature and innane. <br>
<br>
To be a member of Catharsis is to know that you are among friends that will drop what they are doing and come to your aid at any time, for any reason.<br>
<br>
I hope that clears up some misperceptions and sparks some intrest for some of you in our team.<br>
<br>
I wish you well, and Halcyon<br>
<br>
